    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives but has some mechanical issues that may require attention. There is noticeable cosmetic wear including scratches and interior wear beyond normal use. It is functional for basic transportation but is not in the same condition as a well-maintained vehicle. Buyers should be prepared for some repair costs.",
