    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a fixer-upper or a budget project car? Here's your chance! This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 we want to be upfront with you: it has significant wear, mechanical issues that will need attention, and visible cosmetic damage inside and out. It's not a daily driver as-is, but for the right buyer \u2014 a DIY mechanic, a parts hunter, or someone with a vision \u2014 there's real opportunity here. What you see is what you get, and the price reflects that honestly. Come take a look and decide for yourself!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in mint condition, and I want to give any potential buyer a full and honest picture of just how exceptional this car truly is. The engine runs flawlessly \u2014 smooth, responsive, and powerful \u2014 with no hesitation, unusual noises, or warning lights of any kind. The transmission shifts crisply and cleanly through all gears, and every mechanical system, including brakes, suspension, steering, and cooling, is functioning exactly as it should. The exterior is in outstanding shape: the paint retains its original deep luster with no fading, scratches, chips, or dents to speak of. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 the upholstery, dashboard, trim, and carpeting all look and feel virtually new, with no staining, cracking, or wear. All electronics, including the infotainment system, climate control, windows, locks, and lights, work perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and is ready to drive with complete confidence from day one.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Honest Value & Solid Bones \u2014 A Practical Pick for the Right Buyer! \ud83d\ude97 Here's a straightforward opportunity for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price tag! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, and has been used regularly, though it does show some signs of wear and age you'd expect at this price point. There are a few cosmetic imperfections and minor mechanical items worth noting, so we'd recommend a pre-purchase inspection to know exactly what you're getting. That said, this car offers real everyday utility and a lot of value for the money. Come take a look \u2014 we're happy to answer any questions honestly! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is priced accordingly. It represents a practical, budget-conscious option for buyers who need reliable transportation and don't mind some cosmetic and mechanical imperfections. The exterior shows visible signs of wear \u2014 there are several scratches, minor dents, and areas where the paint has faded or chipped, giving the body a well-used appearance. The interior is functional but shows its age, with worn upholstery, some scuffs on the dashboard and door panels, and general signs of everyday use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but prospective buyers should be aware that it may require some maintenance or repairs in the near term \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic. There are no major structural or safety issues that we are aware of, but this is not a turn-key, worry-free vehicle. It's best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project car or someone looking for basic, affordable transportation with the understanding that additional investment may be needed.",
      "price": 21000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This dependable vehicle arrives in solid good condition, offering a well-maintained interior and a mechanically sound drivetrain that's ready for the road. Exterior shows the expected character marks of a pre-owned vehicle, but nothing that detracts from its everyday appeal or reliability. Serviced and inspected, this is a smart, honest choice for the value-conscious buyer who wants confidence without the premium price tag of a showroom model.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! \ud83d\ude97 I've got a fantastic ride here that I'm genuinely excited to pass along to its next happy owner. This beauty is in great shape \u2014 she's been well cared for, drives smooth, and is ready to hit the road without missing a beat. Sure, she's got a little character from her time on the road (what car doesn't after a few years?), but nothing that takes away from the joy of driving her. Mechanically sound, clean interior, and she turns heads wherever she goes. I'm the kind of seller who believes in keeping things simple and honest \u2014 what you see is what you get, and what you get here is a really solid car at a fair price. Come take her for a spin and I think you'll fall in love just like I did. Serious buyers, reach out \u2014 I'd love to find her a good home! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Rolling out of our inventory is this exceptionally sorted machine, presenting with a drivetrain that pulls cleanly through the entire RPM band \u2014 throttle response is crisp, transmission shifts are deliberate and positive, and the suspension geometry remains tight with no perceptible slop in the steering rack. The engine bay shows the kind of honest patina you'd expect from a vehicle that's been *driven*, not babied, but mechanically it's dialed in. Braking feel is progressive and confident, rotors are within spec, and the cooling system maintains optimal thermal management under load. Interior surfaces show light use-wear consistent with active ownership \u2014 nothing that detracts from the driving experience. This is a driver's car priced for a driver who knows what to look for under the hood. Serious inquiries only \u2014 this one won't sit long.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    }
  ],
